{"tid":325548,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場客運大樓內用航拍機自拍 Selfie男回港即被捕","createTime":"2017-07-17T10:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T10:33:09.000Z","uid":33373,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"abd0576267d236581c54b0b6601e4f8428a9b524","tid":325548,"uid":33373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T10:00:28.000Z","msg":"51歲姓楊男子，涉嫌於上周四(13日)下午1時30分，於香港國際機場中場客運廊禁區內，將一架航拍機搖控至空中進行拍攝，並將相片上載至fb，警方接報進行調查。楊今日中午抵港後，即被警方拘捕，他涉嫌危害航行安全，案件交機場警區刑事情報及支援組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港法例第483A章《機場管理局附例》第35條危害航行安全，一經定罪最高刑罰為罰款港幣50,000元及監禁六6個月。警方呼籲市民，任何人不得在機場範圍內放模型飛機及進行航拍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>抵死</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7efc7580b1db907951814cfc3f74ee54b25ccbff","tid":325548,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T10:04:29.000Z","msg":"點解警察會知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc2e0c76c03e719c7b5d9977fea0da4989c391e1","tid":325548,"uid":8414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T10:05:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解警察會知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驗眼"},{"pid":"57a9bad1610da41238132e81be1dc02c5a4d65cf","tid":325548,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T10:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解警察會知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放上facebook"},{"pid":"3c307ea1d8c1bd6fb1907c2798e826861db84761","tid":325548,"uid":3399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T10:06:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解警察會知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n並將相片上載至fb，警方接報進行調查"},{"pid":"80988a8a50f339ccdbecb1134412cf759ce09992","tid":325548,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T10:08:25.000Z","msg":"五十幾歲都咁on9"},{"pid":"34ba823a4e3b40f4aa3f